name: Increase Max HP
notes:
Gain +3 to your maximum HP. 
*Once your maximum HP is equal to or greater than 60, this only grants +2 towards your maximum HP.
**Once your maximum HP is equal to or greater than 90, this only grants +1 towards your maximum HP.

name: Increase Movement Speed
notes:
Gain +0.5 to your maximum Movement Speed. 
*Once your maximum Speed is equal to or greater than 10, this only grants +0.25 towards your maximum Speed.

name: Increase Max MP
notes:
Gain +2 to your maximum MP
*Once your maximum MP is equal to or greater than 50, this only grants +1 towards your maximum MP.

name: Focus Level 1
notes: Gain a +1 focus for a single attribute test. This grants you +1 on all test results towards tests relevant to your focus.

name: Focus Level 2
notes: Upgrade your +1 focus to be a +2 focus.

name: Focus Level 3
notes: Upgrade your +2 focus to be a +3 focus.

name: Talent Level
notes: Gain the Novice abilities for a new talent, or the next level of a talent you already have.

name: Specialization Level
notes: Gain a new Specialization, or the next level of a Specialization you already have.

name: Endurance
notes:
The cost to increase this attribute is equivalent to the level of the attribute you are attempting to gain. Minimum 2 points. 
Example 1: you currently have 2 End and you want 3 End, this will cost 3 points. 
Example 2: you currently have 0 Dex and want 1 Dex, this will cost 2 points. (minimum of 2)

name: Basic Spell
notes: Learn a basic level spell from any school of magic.

name: Novice Spell
notes: Learn a novice level spell from any school of magic.

name: Adept Spell
notes: Learn an Adept level spell for a school of magic that you already know at least one novice spell in.

name: Master Spell
notes: Learn a Master level spell for a school of magic that you already know at least one Adept level spell in.
